<p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; line-height: 24px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; color: #1c3f94;">Dear {{lead.First Name:default=Friend}},</p>
<p style="color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-top: 15px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: left;">Thank you for requesting your free consultation from Direct Energy Solar and for taking the time to discuss your energy needs with us. Your Solar Consultant was happy to share how much money you&rsquo;ll save on your electricity bill by going solar with us. We hope to have the opportunity to become your chosen solar installer.</p>
<p style="color: #1c3f94; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; line-height: 30px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 25px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: left;">You have qualified for a 6-month Heating &amp; Cooling Repair Essentials Plan from Direct Energy</p>
<p style="color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-top: 15px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: left;">At Direct Energy Solar, providing our customers with peace of mind is important to us&mdash;from our going solar process to our warranties and guarantees. As a part of the Direct Energy family, we are proud to offer you even further peace of mind with a special offer from Direct Energy Protection Plans.</p>
<p style="color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-top: 15px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: left;">As a thank you for meeting with a Direct Energy Solar consultant, you have qualified for a Free* 6-month Heating &amp; Cooling Repair Essentials Plan. This plan provides worry-free coverage for inconvenient repairs.</p>
<p style="color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-top: 15px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: left;">You will be soon be receiving by mail, if you have not already, a welcome kit from Direct Energy Protection Plans that includes coverage and other details about your plan. Please enjoy this special offer, with our compliments.</p>
